cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with object detection and segmentation. It also incorporates machine learning techniques such as curriculum learning (cs.LG) and multiple instance learning (cs.AI). Additionally, it may fall under multimedia (cs.MM) as it deals with image analysis and recognition. Finally, it may also be related to neural networks (cs.NE) as deep learning methods are commonly used in object detection and segmentation tasks.
